ckground-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">President of Pakistan</a></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-bottom: none;\"><span class=\"nowrap\" style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"><b>In office</b></span><br>11 August 1947&nbsp;– 11 September 1948</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left;\">Deputy</th><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liaquat_Ali_Khan\" title=\"Liaquat Ali Khan\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Liaquat Ali Khan</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left;\"><span class=\"nowrap\" style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">Preceded by</span></th><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Office created</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left;\"><span class=\"nowrap\" style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">Succeeded by</span></th><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Office abolished</td></tr></tbody></table>');
