title=\"Caretaker Prime Minister of Pakistan\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Acting</a>)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; background: lavender; line-height: normal; padding: 0.2em;\">Chairman of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pakistan_Tehreek-e-Insaf\" title=\"Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf</a></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-bottom: none;\"><div style=\"width: 291px; margin: 0px; background-color: lavender;\"><b><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Incumbent\" title=\"Incumbent\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Incumbent</a></b></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-bottom: none;\"><span class=\"nowrap\" style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"><b>Assumed office</b></span><br>25 April 1996</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left;\">Deputy</th><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shah_Mehmood_Qureshi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shah Mehmood Qureshi\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Shah Mehmood Qureshi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left;\"><span class=\"nowrap\" style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">Preceded by</span></th><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Position established</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; background: lavender; line-height: normal; padding: 0.2em;\">Member of the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Assembly_of_Pakistan\" title=\"National Assembly of Pakistan\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">National Assembly</a></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-bottom: none;\"><div style=\"width: 291px; margin: 0px; background-color: lavender;\"><b><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Incumbent\" title=\"Incumbent\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Incumbent</a></b></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; border-bottom: none;\"><span class=\"nowrap\" style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"><b>Assumed office</b></span><br>13 August 2018</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: left;\"><span class=\"nowrap\" style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">Preceded by</span></th><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Obaidullah_Shadikhel\" title=\"Obaidullah Shadikhel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Obaidullah Shadikhel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"r